item.title: Marriage Licence Statistics
item.description: Abstract There are thousands of couples are getting married each day in the world. We are curious about how many marriage licenses are issued daily in Toronto. This paper, we explore the number of marriage licences which are issued each week with the collected data from the January of 2011 to the August of 2020. In our table, the data is collected every week of the month. The data provider divides one month into four weeks.
